A huge storm is coming at 11:07.
We're gonna be in deep shit.

2087
01:43:20.166 --> 01:43:21.250
-[laughs]
-Let's go!

2088
01:43:21.791 --> 01:43:24.458
-We're in deep shit!
-[laughing]

2089
01:43:24.541 --> 01:43:26.625
