2150
01:47:07.541 --> 01:47:09.541
-[woman] No!
-[man 3] Watch out!

2151
01:47:12.583 --> 01:47:13.583
Look out!

2152
01:47:18.791 --> 01:47:20.458
[loud bang]

2153
01:47:26.708 --> 01:47:28.583
[clattering]

2154
01:47:30.166 --> 01:47:32.583
