2157
01:47:40.833 --> 01:47:41.666
[man screams]

2158
01:47:48.083 --> 01:47:49.375
Ah!

2159
01:47:49.458 --> 01:47:50.541
[hail smashing]

2160
01:47:53.458 --> 01:47:54.791
