2161
01:47:56.250 --> 01:47:58.458
-[metal clanging]
-[glass shattering]

2162
01:47:58.541 --> 01:48:01.666
THE GREAT WEATHER SHOW
AT 9:45 ON TL10

2163
01:48:02.791 --> 01:48:04.291
[shattering]

2164
01:48:05.291 --> 01:48:06.958
[alarm blaring]

2165
01:48:12.708 --> 01:48:14.000
[Gustavo sighs]

2166
