[tires screech]

2172
01:49:05.500 --> 01:49:06.875
[ice cracking]

2173
01:49:09.208 --> 01:49:11.916
-[water dripping]
-[alarms blaring]

2174
01:49:13.583 --> 01:49:14.708
[ice clatters]

2175
01:49:14.791 --> 01:49:17.291
[dramatic music playing]

2176
01:49:59.583 --> 01:50:02.500
[music swells]

2177
01:50:23.416 --> 01:50:25.958
