2181
01:50:34.375 --> 01:50:35.500
<i>but let's focus on…</i>

2182
01:50:35.583 --> 01:50:37.166
This one or this one. Miguel?

2183
01:50:38.375 --> 01:50:39.541
-That one.
-Great.

2184
01:50:39.625 --> 01:50:40.625
