2191
01:51:20.625 --> 01:51:21.875
Good.

2192
01:51:21.958 --> 01:51:23.375
Can I sit?

2193
01:51:24.125 --> 01:51:25.416
Yes. Of course.

2194
01:51:25.500 --> 01:51:26.458
Yes.

2195
01:51:27.916 --> 01:51:28.958
